    Ensures only correct type is allowed at compile time
    🔹 Without Generics
            List list = new ArrayList();
            list.add("Java");
            list.add(10); // allowed ❌
    🔹 With Generics
            List<String> list = new ArrayList<>();
            list.add("Java");
